A vintage-style illustrated blueprint showing an intricate skill tree or technology map rendered as an antique cartographer's chart, with interconnected pathways branching out like a sprawling transit system. The map features small iconic symbols representing different technical domains - gears, code brackets, network nodes, and document icons - connected by flowing lines in sepia, navy, and gold tones. The pathways converge toward a central ornate compass rose. Weathered parchment texture with elegant decorative borders featuring small technical motifs. Soft vignetting around edges gives depth. The overall feeling evokes both the complexity of mastering a craft and the adventure of learning, like an explorer's guide to a vast technical landscape.
